commit.message: upgrade META_ADD/MERGE properly when 2.0 elements are found
set dynamic_config to false by default
make sure at least the same version of EUMM::CPANfile is used to install
make sure cpanfile is in the same directory as Makefile.PL, and otherwise, return or exit correctly
lowered the version requirement in cpanfile for testing
lowered the version requirement of EUMM to 6.17, the one bundled in Perl 5.8.1
prevent WriteMakefile from dying because of unknown keys
as we load EUMM internally, we don't need to use it explicitly in Makefile.PL
added an author test to see if EUMM::CPANfile works with older EUMMs
